						<div class="postbody">Look at a 6502 manual, There are opcodes for specific operations like this!<br /><br />They are Branching Instrucions!<br /><br />EDIT:<br /><br />IF Carry Set = BCS<br />IF Equal = BEQ<br />IF Less = BMI(?)</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />AKA SmilyMZX/AtariHacker.</div>
